        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Andrea <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">rimase</span> a bocca aperta perché il quadro <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="purple">era bellissimo</span>.</span>
