      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
        <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il mio gatto <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="purple">è vivace</span> e <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">salta</span> qua e là tutto il giorno.</span>
